Abbaye waa mba pa-hɩla kɩla kʊyʊʊ yɔ pɛ-tɛ pɛ-tɛ yɔ Prüm, Ratisbonne, Fulda, Ellwang, Salzbourg, Reichenau, Beuron, Hirsau, Metten, Scheyern, Ettal, Ottobeuren, Einsiedeln, Admont, Melk. [[Englɩsɩɩ kʊnʊŋ|Ɛngɩlɩsɩ]] ɛjaɖɛ taa lɛ, Benoît maacɔ waa kuduyiŋ weyi ɛ-hɩla kɩla sɛʊʊ yɔ ɛlɛ wɛɛ tɛtʊ naa pɛ nɛ pa-taa Cantorbéry, York, Westminster, Saint-Albans. [[Pɛliziki|Pɛlɩzɩkɩ]] ɛjaɖɛ taa lɛ ɖɩnaɣ Maredsous abbaye yaa Strvelot ñɩŋʊ.
